00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,520
 He prays to God.

422
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:10,200
 He says, "You told me to return to my country

423
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,520
 "that you would do good.

424
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,600
 "I'm not worthy of the least of the deeds

425
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:15,440
 "of your steadfast love and all your faithfulness

426
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,060
 "that you've shown me.

427
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:20,440
 "For even though when I only had my staff,

