00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,600
 I mean, what would happen if we did this?

444
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:06,360
 If there's something that's found

445
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:11,360
 when we turn our dependence on God into a prayer to God?

446
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:14,280
 What if that's what prayer really is about,

447
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:18,800
 being honest with him and being honest with yourself,

448
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:20,600
 that perhaps you've not been worthy,

449
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,920
 but actually God's been good.

450
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,000
 God has done things.

451
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,780
 It's fascinating.

452
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:29,080
 Jacob is at this point where he might get killed

453
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:31,360
 and everything he has might be destroyed,

454
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:33,440
 and he recounts the blessings of God.

