00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:41,400
 I just had the clothes on my back and that's it.

459
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:43,560
 But now I'm here with two camps.

460
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:46,320
 He's speaking of the wealth that he's accumulated,

461
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:47,880
 of family, children.

462
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:50,200
 He has been blessed.

463
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:53,800
 And he's thanking God, first and foremost,

