00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:34,440
 Now the big, the encounter comes

500
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,080
 because he opens himself up.

501
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:38,480
 He prays, nothing happens.

502
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:41,880
 In the moment of praying, there's no big miracle or anything

