00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:53,280
 See, after his prayer, I love this as well,

506
00:20:53,280 --> 00:20:54,600
 the Bible doesn't sugarcoat things.

507
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:56,800
 Genesis is for us broken people, right?

508
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:59,160
 Jacob has this prayer, he's thanked God,

509
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:02,000
 he's been honest with God and I think for lots of us,

510
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:03,760
 we think that if we just do it like that,

